sequenceDiagram
   participant Student
   participant FocusTimeSystem
   participant AuthService
   participant Database


   Student->>FocusTimeSystem: Enter Credentials
   activate FocusTimeSystem
   FocusTimeSystem->>AuthService: Validate Credentials
   activate AuthService
   AuthService->>Database: Query User Data
   activate Database
   Database-->>AuthService: Return User Info
   deactivate Database
   AuthService-->>FocusTimeSystem: Authentication Result
   deactivate AuthService
   FocusTimeSystem-->>Student: Grant Access / Show Dashboard
   deactivate FocusTimeSystem
